OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A simple law change around prescribing 
OL,6, could help ease the treatment crisis   
OL,7, facing many women going through the    
OL,8, menopause, the Royal College of        
OL,9, Pharmacists says.                      
OL,11,FSome are now struggling with untreated 
OL,12,Fsymptoms due to shortages of some types
OL,13,Fof hormone-replacement therapy (HRT).  
OL,15,FWomen who rely on the medicine have    
OL,16,Freported feeling suicidal without it.  
OL,18,FThe RPS wants pharmacists in England to
OL,19,Fbe able to alter GP prescriptions and  
OL,20,Fmake medicine swaps when appropriate.  
